Now, be smart, or it won't just be you.

59:48.255 --> 59:49.856
It'll be your wife and babies too.

59:49.956 --> 59:52.292
Get in the car. Get in the car.

59:58.165 --> 59:59.299
Through this holy anointing,

59:59.399 --> 01:00:01.201
may the Lord in his love and mercy

01:00:01.301 --> 01:00:03.970
help you with the grace of the holy spirit.

01:00:04.070 --> 01:00:05.972
May the lord who frees you from sin

01:00:06.072 --> 01:00:08.441
save you and raise you up.

01:00:11.811 --> 01:00:14.080
Jocelyn?

01:00:14.181 --> 01:00:16.283
I'm ready.

01:00:23.890 --> 01:00:25.158
Get away from my son.

01:00:25.258 --> 01:00:26.559
What the hell are you doing here?

01:00:26.659 --> 01:00:28.795
I told you that he wasn't allowed in here.

01:00:28.895 --> 01:00:30.096
- It's not up to her.
- What?

01:00:30.197 --> 01:00:31.464
This is a 48-hour stay of the court,

01:00:31.564 --> 01:00:33.166
during which time you're required to keep

01:00:33.266 --> 01:00:35.435
Pernell Harris Junior
connected to a ventilator

01:00:35.535 --> 01:00:38.738
and take all necessary
measures to keep him alive.

01:00:38.838 --> 01:00:40.673
He's already dead.

01:00:40.773 --> 01:00:43.376
You're going to thank me for this one day.

01:00:43.476 --> 01:00:46.213
Why are you doing this me? Why?

01:00:46.246 --> 01:00:47.880
Why? Why are you doing this?

01:00:47.980 --> 01:00:49.882
Why? Why?

01:00:49.982 --> 01:00:50.917
Why? Why?

01:00:51.017 --> 01:00:53.453
Because I believe in miracles.

01:00:53.553 --> 01:00:55.455
♪ Have along for the ride ♪

01:00:55.555 --> 01:00:58.691
♪ If you make the decisions,
I'll be right by your side ♪

01:00:58.791 --> 01:01:02.495
♪ You want to show me
how you like to get high ♪

01:01:02.595 --> 01:01:08.868
♪ Well, I've already seen it
but I'll go back and try ♪

01:01:08.968 --> 01:01:13.072
♪ Try again ♪

01:01:13.240 --> 01:01:16.476
♪ I'll try, try again ♪

01:01:16.576 --> 01:01:20.547
What you're describing is
called an acute stress reaction.

01:01:20.647 --> 01:01:23.350
It's a common reaction to traumatic events.

01:01:23.450 --> 01:01:26.519
The more extreme the event,
the more extreme the reaction.

01:01:26.619 --> 01:01:28.255
Praise God!

01:01:28.288 --> 01:01:32.024
Praise God! Praise God!

01:01:32.124 --> 01:01:34.661
God worked a miracle today!

01:01:34.761 --> 01:01:36.763
Yes, he did.

01:01:38.798 --> 01:01:41.768
Literally reached down

01:01:41.868 --> 01:01:44.003
and made his will be done.

01:01:44.103 --> 01:01:45.872
That's right.

01:01:45.972 --> 01:01:48.040
And he used this man to do it.

01:01:48.140 --> 01:01:49.976
In some cases, a person's reality

01:01:50.076 --> 01:01:51.511
can actually be altered.

01:01:51.611 --> 01:01:54.080
It's easier than you think for imagination

01:01:54.180 --> 01:01:55.782
to become hallucination.

01:01:55.882 --> 01:01:57.884
Come on up, brother Pernell!

01:01:57.984 --> 01:02:01.087
You testify! Testify!

01:02:01.187 --> 01:02:02.489
Tell them your story.

01:02:02.589 --> 01:02:06.158
Tell them your story. Thank you, Jesus!

01:02:12.699 --> 01:02:16.002
I don't know exactly what to say,

01:02:16.102 --> 01:02:18.305
except, um...

01:02:19.539 --> 01:02:22.008
God just taught me the miracle of life.

01:02:25.612 --> 01:02:27.714
Of course he thinks they're real.

01:02:27.814 --> 01:02:31.150
The hallucinations activate
the same perceptual systems

01:02:31.318 --> 01:02:32.652
of the brain as reality.

01:02:32.752 --> 01:02:34.754
Please, just tell me there's a pill.

01:02:34.854 --> 01:02:37.490
I'm not a good man.

01:02:37.590 --> 01:02:39.359
I drink, I whore, I lie.

01:02:39.459 --> 01:02:40.760
We're all sinners saved by grace.

01:02:40.860 --> 01:02:42.395
Amen.

01:02:42.495 --> 01:02:47.834
Before last week, I was
only in church two times.

01:02:47.934 --> 01:02:51.338
One for my wedding...

01:02:51.371 --> 01:02:53.340
And one for my mother's funeral.

01:02:53.406 --> 01:02:55.808
That's okay. Jesus loves you.

01:02:55.908 --> 01:02:56.843
- Amen.
- Amen.

01:02:56.943 --> 01:02:58.678
Yes, he does. Amen.

01:02:58.778 --> 01:03:00.513
Medication won't be nearly enough.

01:03:00.613 --> 01:03:04.951
He needs to be treated by a
professional in a hospital.

01:03:07.487 --> 01:03:09.722
I didn't rape that girl.

01:03:09.822 --> 01:03:13.225
I didn't rape anybody. I swear to God.

01:03:13.360 --> 01:03:14.994
Stop lying, Shane.

01:03:15.094 --> 01:03:18.831
I know the truth.

01:03:18.931 --> 01:03:20.400
You raped that woman,

01:03:20.500 --> 01:03:22.268
and now God wants you struck down.

01:03:22.369 --> 01:03:24.771
No! God would never tell anybody

01:03:24.871 --> 01:03:26.873
to kill somebody.

01:03:26.973 --> 01:03:28.575
God is love.

01:03:28.675 --> 01:03:33.780
Well, you got to brush up
on your Bible studies, boy.

01:03:36.248 --> 01:03:38.050
"Rejoice with him, o, heavens;

01:03:38.150 --> 01:03:40.219
"Bow down to him, all gods,

01:03:40.387 --> 01:03:42.422
"For he avenges the
blood of his children,

01:03:42.522 --> 01:03:44.023
and takes vengeance on
his adversaries."

01:03:44.123 --> 01:03:47.527
- Wait, please...
- He repays those who hate him.

01:03:47.627 --> 01:03:49.429
Just listen to me... God, please!

01:03:49.529 --> 01:03:50.863
And cleanses his people's land.

01:03:50.963 --> 01:03:51.964
Aah!

01:04:02.909 --> 01:04:05.678
I don't know the Bible like I should.

01:04:05.778 --> 01:04:07.947
I don't even know the Lord's prayer.

01:04:08.047 --> 01:04:09.982
God sees your heart.

01:04:10.082 --> 01:04:11.851
But I do know this.

01:04:11.951 --> 01:04:13.420
- God called.
- Yes.

01:04:13.520 --> 01:04:16.188
- Praise Jesus.
- Amen.

01:04:16.288 --> 01:04:17.924
And I answered.

01:04:18.024 --> 01:04:20.893
Amen! Praise God!

01:04:22.429 --> 01:04:24.296
Hallelujah! Amen!

01:04:24.431 --> 01:04:27.133
You can still go to heaven, Shane.

01:04:27.233 --> 01:04:28.835
Do you want to?

01:04:36.075 --> 01:04:37.644
Yeah.

01:04:43.450 --> 01:04:48.688
Do you accept Jesus as your lord and savior?

01:04:48.788 --> 01:04:49.956
Okay.

01:04:50.056 --> 01:04:51.357
Say "I do."

01:04:51.458 --> 01:04:52.592
I do.

01:04:52.692 --> 01:04:57.497
Say "Dear Lord,
please forgive me."

01:04:57.597 --> 01:04:58.998
- Jesus!
- Saves!

01:04:59.098 --> 01:05:00.299
- Jesus!
- Saves!

01:05:00.467 --> 01:05:02.835
- Jesus!
- Saves!

01:05:06.238 --> 01:05:12.078
Dear Lord, please forgive me.

01:05:12.178 --> 01:05:15.982
They made me rape her.

01:05:16.082 --> 01:05:18.184
What did you say?

01:05:18.284 --> 01:05:20.553
I just wanted to get the book,

01:05:20.653 --> 01:05:23.590
but they said that I had to rape her.

01:05:23.690 --> 01:05:26.325
- Who's they?
- I had to do it that way.

01:05:26.493 --> 01:05:30.296
- Who's they?
- Dear Lord...

01:05:30.396 --> 01:05:32.665
Please forgive me.

01:05:32.765 --> 01:05:34.801
No. Who's they?

01:05:34.901 --> 01:05:37.103
Who made you?

